OL,3,CHome Secretary wants jailed ex-Labour
OL,4,CMP to resign or face recall petition
OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper says she
OL,7,Fwants to see jailed MP Mike Amesbury
OL,8,Fresign or face a recall petition.
OL,10,FHer comments come as the former Labour
OL,11,FMP was jailed for 10 weeks for
OL,12,Fpunching a man after a row in the
OL,13,Fstreet in Frodsham, Cheshire.
OL,15,FThe sentence leaves him at risk of
OL,16,Fbeing ousted if his constituents back
OL,17,Fa petition calling for a by-election
OL,18,Fbut opposition parties have demanded
OL,19,Fhis immediate resignation.
