OL,6,FMs Cooper was asked for a response on
OL,7,FAmesbury continuing to be an MP and
OL,8,Freceiving full pay as there is no
OL,9,Fautomatic suspension for MPs serving a
OL,10,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,12,F"I think you're asking me about
OL,13,Fparliamentary rules and procedure,
OL,14,Fwhich are obviously separate from
OL,15,Fthose that the Government runs ... I'm
OL,16,Fmaking my view clear, which is that I
OL,17,Fwant to see the people of Runcorn get
OL,18,Fnew representation as swiftly as
OL,19,Fpossible."
