OL,6,FAmesbury pleaded guilty at a hearing
OL,7,Fin January to assault and was
OL,8,Fsentenced on Monday 24 February at
OL,9,FChester Magistrates' Court.
OL,11,FAn application for bail, pending an
OL,12,Fappeal against his sentence, was
OL,13,Frefused by the judge.
OL,15,FFootage recorded on a mobile phone
OL,16,Fshows the aftermath of the assault
