OL,3,CHome Secretary wants jailed ex-Labour
OL,4,CMP to resign or face recall petition
OL,6,FAmesbury's sentence will be served at
OL,7,FHMP Altcourse in Liverpool. It leaves
OL,8,Fhim liable to the recall process,
OL,9,Fwhich would trigger a by-election if
OL,10,F10% of registered voters in his
OL,11,Fconstituency sign a petition calling
OL,12,Ffor it. As long as he remains an MP he
OL,13,Fwill continue to be paid his salary.
OL,15,FAny custodial sentence of less than a
OL,16,Fyear, even it if is suspended, would
OL,17,Ftrigger the recall process but it will
OL,18,Fonly begin after all appeals have been
OL,19,Fexhausted.
