OL,6,FIn 2024 Amesbury won Runcorn and
OL,7,FHelsby with a majority of 14,696 over
OL,8,FReform UK.
OL,10,FA Labour Party spokesperson said on
OL,11,FMonday that the party took "swift
OL,12,Faction" following his "completely
OL,13,Funacceptable actions".
OL,15,FThe spokesperson said his constituents
OL,16,F"deserved better".
